who are not doing this.

01:03:42.860 --> 01:03:47.160
But these two patients who
they studied, had that.

01:03:47.160 --> 01:03:48.380
And they got in lots
of trouble in

01:03:48.380 --> 01:03:49.220
school, all the time.

01:03:49.220 --> 01:03:51.770
They did all the things
you might imagine a

01:03:51.770 --> 01:03:53.660
three-year-old, and for
the rest of us, like

01:03:53.660 --> 01:03:55.700
Phineas Gage would do.

01:03:55.700 --> 01:03:57.890
So that raises the question
about whether the kinds of

01:03:57.890 --> 01:04:02.020
